def clean_data(df):
    df = df.str.lower()
    df = df.replace(r'[^--a-zA-Z]', ' ', regex = True)
    df = df.str.strip()
    stop_words = stopwords.words("russian")
    df = df.apply(lambda x: ' '.join([word for word in x.split() if word not in (stop_words)]))
    return df
In [16]:
